name: formSymmetricDifference(_:)
desc: Removes the elements of the set that are also in the given set and adds the members of the given set that are not already in the set.Required. Default implementation provided.

items.name: func formSymmetricDifference(Self)
items.desc: Replaces this set with a new set containing all elements contained in either this set or the given set, but not in both.
